# Routing for the claim CI lanes. Both lanes look up the owner of each claim's *file*
# here and @-mention them on the finding, so drift lands in front of whoever owns the
# decision it rested on. Last matching pattern wins (GitHub's CODEOWNERS rule).
#
# Own your claims by the same paths you own your code: a claim about payments lives
# under the payments path and routes to the payments team.

*                       @your-org/eng
.claims/payments/       @your-org/payments
.claims/builds/         @your-org/platform
